	     <tr><td id=headerrow colspan=2 class=mform valign=top><a name=classes.html?class=8&mid=96659111917064>&nbsp;</a><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=8&mid=96659111917064>RE: Group combat</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=8&mid=96659111917064#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a>
